{"tid":1604402,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我叫日本人罷食元氣星巴克算","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:50:04.000Z","uid":68779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b427fcd689e84a6b8207b5b58250b9e4c9e18662","tid":1604402,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"依排咁多文宣，前排又爆有蟲，經理又照比食客，都唔明點解仲夠膽食<br />\n換轉係日本，一早爆大新聞，全日本人都罷食啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/2752/一次不忠-百次不用-揭麥當勞敗走日本真相\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F2752%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%A0-%E7%99%BE%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8-%E6%8F%AD%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%95%97%E8%B5%B0%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1YhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=14e9e8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/2752/一次不忠-百次不用-揭麥當勞敗走日本真相</a><br />\n<br />\n所以依家寧願用同樣時間花係日本文宣算，起碼日本唔會白痴到新聞報哂有蟲壽司，有哂化驗報告，都仲會去食攞自己條命搞。<br />\n同埋日本人真係有團結性，大家話唔食就真係唔食，日本麥當勞已經係成功例子。<br />\n<br />\n除左元氣，我會叫埋日本人罷飲星巴克。日本市場係美國總公司全資擁有，作為佢地既第二大市場，我諗有必要令日本人知道星巴克係其他先進地方竟然會用公廁水沖咖啡。兩件事一次過係日本爆出黎，應該會令日本社會特別關心依兩間公司係當地衛生情況。<br />\n<br />\n再者，日本人都有必要知道依兩間公司既香港合作商(美心)，係一間咩野公司。日本社會咁重視道德觀念，相信佢地會再三考慮會否光顧元氣同星巴克。日本人另一特色係好強烈羞恥心，當全日本都鄙視呢兩間公司時，係冇人去食，因為佢地恥與為伍。<br />\n<br />\n上個post<br />\n[星巴克 元氣員工快入] 美心金蛋就快破裂 [黃之鋒 周庭 快睇]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598939</a>"},{"pid":"349f5cfb21b01b08a5b0fc7ea34e94f176d6a889","tid":1604402,"uid":11291,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"老老實實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢兩年因工作關係香港大阪兩邊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我連邊度有元氣我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8bf6ded091ba1f4719aa2c80ab4d9ace240dc9","tid":1604402,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"349f5cfb21b01b08a5b0fc7ea34e94f176d6a889","tid":1604402,"uid":11291,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"老老實實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢兩年因工作關係香港大阪兩邊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我連邊度有元氣我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"利申：新大阪（仲遠啲兼隔一條河）"},{"pid":"4a4d6c10ae6cd981ea39ea9687d1246a9d087539","tid":1604402,"uid":7198,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"香港人平就得嫁啦<br />\n「比個機會佢啦」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f26cce893ff7d45a00b045a665ce22a13508de6","tid":1604402,"uid":17932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"上次去日本好多人食M記wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265d35b47d0733707db9ff0479fe5f32b7ce78d","tid":1604402,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa259aa825b1f